msgid "Polling interval (ms):"
msgstr "Intervalle de polling (ms) :"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:259
msgid "How often the widget checks if the daemon is running (in milliseconds)."
msgstr ""
"Fréquence de vérification du démon (en millisecondes).Fréquence à laquelle "
"le widget vérifie si le daemon est actif (en millisecondes)."

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:264
msgid "Show last transcription:"
msgstr "Afficher la dernière transcription :"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:270
msgid "Display the last transcribed text in the popup window."
msgstr "Afficher le dernier texte transcrit dans la fenêtre popup."

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:276
msgid "Preview mode (test with mic):"
msgstr "Mode aperçu (test avec micro) :"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:281
msgid "Audio context buffer:"
msgstr "Tampon de contexte audio :"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:286
msgid "Microphone volume:"
msgstr "Volume du microphone :"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:310
msgid ""
"Adjust the microphone input volume (PipeWire/PulseAudio default source)."
msgstr ""
"Ajuster le volume d'entrée du microphone (source par défaut PipeWire/"
"PulseAudio)."

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:316
msgid "Noise floor:"
msgstr "Plancher de bruit :"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:319
msgid "Calibrate"
msgstr "Calibrer"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:322
msgid "Recording silence…"
msgstr "Enregistrement du silence…"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:328
msgid ""
"Record 5 seconds of silence to calibrate the background noise level. This "
"improves animation accuracy."
msgstr ""
"Enregistrer 5 secondes de silence pour calibrer le niveau de bruit ambiant. "
"Cela améliore la précision de l'animation."

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:339
msgid "Noise gate:"
msgstr "Noise gate :"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:353
msgid ""
"Audio levels below this threshold are zeroed. Increase to suppress "
"background noise and get clean silence."
msgstr ""
"Les niveaux audio en dessous de ce seuil sont mis à zéro. Augmentez pour "
"supprimer le bruit de fond et obtenir un silence propre."

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:358
msgid "Envelope shape:"
msgstr "Forme de l'enveloppe :"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:369
msgid "Flat"
msgstr "Plat"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:371
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "Normal"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:377
msgid ""
"Controls the Hanning envelope shape. 0 = flat (uniform bars), 1 = normal, "
"higher = more peaked at the center."
msgstr ""
"Contrôle la forme de l'enveloppe de Hanning. 0 = plat (barres uniformes), 1 "
"= normal, plus élevé = plus pointu au centre."

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:382
msgid "Envelope center:"
msgstr "Centre de l'enveloppe :"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:398
msgid ""
"Shift the envelope peak across the frequency range (80–4000 Hz). Useful with "
"rainbow colors to emphasize different frequency bands."
msgstr ""
"Déplacer le pic de l'enveloppe sur la plage de fréquences (80–4000 Hz). "
"Utile avec les couleurs arc-en-ciel pour accentuer différentes bandes de "
"fréquences."

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:404
msgid "Animation"
msgstr "Animation"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:409
msgid "Reset icon settings:"
msgstr "Réinitialiser l'icône :"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:412
msgid "Reset to defaults"
msgstr "Valeurs par défaut"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:417
msgid ""
"Restore all icon animation settings (style, bars, wave, pulse, dots, "
"waveform, rainbow, sensitivity, envelope, noise gate) to their installation "
"defaults. Other preferences (polling, transcription display, audio context) "
"are not affected."
msgstr ""
"Restaurer tous les réglages d'animation de l'icône (style, barres, onde, "
"pulsation, points, forme d'onde, arc-en-ciel, sensibilité, enveloppe, seuil "
"de bruit) à leurs valeurs par défaut d'installation. Les autres préférences "
"(interrogation, affichage de la transcription, contexte audio) ne sont pas "
"modifiées."

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:423
msgid "Reset icon settings"
msgstr "Réinitialiser l'icône"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:428
msgid ""
"All icon animation settings will be restored to defaults.\n"
"Continue?"
msgstr ""
"Tous les réglages d'animation de l'icône vont être remis aux valeurs par "
"défaut.\n"
"Continuer ?"

